---
title: Greek-Style Eggplant Wedges & Roast Veggies with Parmesan Cheese & Capsicum Relish Aioli
description: Any veggie lover will tell you, eggplant is king of the vegetable castle! With its deep purple hue and spongy texture, it's the chameleon of the kitchen, soaking up flavours and turning every dish into a taste sensation. Serve it with a few other veggie friends and a sprinkling of Parmesan cheese for extra punch!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
